THE GAME
--------

  'Angliant' is a Workbench game in which you rotate tiles that
contain 90 degrees angles, so that an 'X' shape moves from one
tile to another, until it gets to the 'exit' tile. However, the
X shape will move if only one angle is connected with the angle
the X shape is located on...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

